egory:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Osaka Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:Gamba Osaka players]]\n[[Category:Gamba Osaka U-23 players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Ayumu Matsumoto\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Ayumu Matsumoto\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1998|4|28}}\n|birth_place=[[Osaka Prefecture|Osaka]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.77}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=[[Gamba Osaka]]\n|clubnumber=44\n|youthyears1=|youthclubs1=[[Gamba Osaka]]\n|years1=2016\u2013|clubs1=[[Gamba Osaka U-23]]|caps1=2|goals1=0\n|totalcaps=2|totalgoals=0\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update= 31 December 2016\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Ayumu Matsumoto'''|\u677e\u672c \u6b69\u5922|Matsumoto Ayumu|born April 28, 1998}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=19428 J.League Data Site]</ref> He plays for [[Gamba Osaka]].\n\n==Career==\nAyumu Matsumoto joined [[Gamba Osaka]] in 2016. On April 3, he debuted in [[J3 League]] (v [[Kataller Toyama]]).<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=19428 J.League Data Site]</ref><ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFMS02/?match_card_id=18684 Match report J.League Data Site]</ref>\n\n;Reserves performance\n\nLast Updated: 31 December 2016\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Season !! Club !! League\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Japan\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | To